    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## What is a PromptTemplate?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "**Mad Libs for AI prompts!**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "- üìù **Template** with placeholder variables",
        "- üîÑ **Reusable** across different inputs",
        "- ‚úÖ **Consistent** prompt structure",
        "- üéØ **Dynamic** content injection"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## What is an LLMChain?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "- üîó **Combines** PromptTemplate + LLM + Output Parser",
        "- ‚ö° **Single call** to run the entire pipeline",
        "- üéõÔ∏è **Configurable** - swap models easily",
        "- üìä **Trackable** - debug each step"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Real-World Example"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "**Email Marketing Generator:**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Template: \"Write a {tone} email for {audience} about {product} with {call_to_action}\""
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "**Usage:**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "- Professional email for executives about CRM Software",
        "- Friendly email for students about Study App",
        "- Urgent email for customers about Security Update"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "üéØ **One template, endless variations!**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Code Demo: Basic Template"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "!pip install langchain_community\n",
        "!pip install -U langchain-deepseek\n",
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "!pip install langchain_community\n",
        "!pip install -U langchain-deepseek\n",
        "\n",
        "from langchain_deepseek import ChatDeepSeek\n",
        "from langchain.prompts import PromptTemplate\n",
        "from google.colab import userdata\n",
        "\n",
        "# 1Ô∏è‚É£ Initialize the DeepSeek model\n",
        "llm = ChatDeepSeek(\n",
        "    model=\"deepseek-chat\",\n",
        "    temperature=0.7,\n",
        "    max_tokens=None,\n",
        "    timeout=None,\n",
        "    max_retries=2,\n",
        "    api_key=userdata.get('DEEPSEEK_API_KEY')\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "# 2Ô∏è‚É£ Create a prompt template\n",
        "prompt = PromptTemplate(\n",
        "    input_variables=[\"role\", \"task\", \"context\", \"user_input\"],\n",
        "    template=\"\"\"\nYou are a {role}. Your task is to {task}.\nContext: {context}\nUser Input: {user_input}\n\nGenerate a helpful response.\n\"\"\"\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "# 3Ô∏è‚É£ Combine prompt + LLM (pipeline style)\n",
        "chain = prompt | llm"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Input ‚Üí Output Flow"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "**Input:**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "result = chain.invoke({\n",
        "    \"role\": \"marketing\",\n",
        "    \"task\": \"write social media posts\",\n",
        "    \"context\": \"product launch\",\n",
        "    \"user_input\": \"New AI-powered fitness app\"\n",
        "})\n",
        "\n",
        "print(result)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "**Output:**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "> \"üöÄ Introducing FitAI! Revolutionize your workout with personalized AI coaching. Download now and transform your fitness journey! #FitAI #FitnessRevolution\""
      ]
    },
